TodoMVC comparison
====================

Collect and present stats of TodoMVC implementations.
This should be run with [doit](http://pydoit.org)

LOC count by http://cloc.sourceforge.net

install
---------

  $ apt-get install cloc
  $ pip install -r requirements.txt


generate stats
----------------

  $ doit

json output at `stats-data.js`


view
--------

HTML report can be viewed on `compare.html'


